3. Automated Leave, Attendance & Workload Balancing System
Problem Description
Leave approvals often ignore team workload and project deadlines.
Project Objective
To build an intelligent leave management system integrated with project planning.
Key Features
• Leave request portal
• Workload analyzer
• Team calendar
• Auto-approval engine
• Manager dashboard
• Impact visualization
Functional Requirements
• Submit leave requests
• Validate against deadlines
• Display team availability
• Auto-approve based on rules
• Send approval notifications
• Maintain leave history
Non-Functional Requirements
• High accuracy
• Real-time updates
• Data privacy
• System reliability
• Low downtime
Technical Challenges
• Calendar synchronization
• Rule engine design
• Handling peak requests
• Data consistency
